thread.title: BRIEF-Capstar Financial Holdings Reports Q4 Adjusted Earnings Per Share $0.28

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Capstar Financial Holdings Reports Q4 Adjusted Earnings Per Share $0.28
text:
Jan 25 (Reuters) - Capstar Financial Holdings Inc:
* CAPSTAR FINANCIAL HOLDINGS, INC. ANNOUNCES FOURTH QUARTER 2017 RESULTS
* Q4 ADJUSTED EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.28 * Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.01 * Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $0.26 -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* CAPSTAR - EXPECTS REVALUATION OF NET DEFERRED TAX ASSET POSITION TO RESULT IN ONE-TIME, NON-CASH CHARGE OF ABOUT $3.6 MILLION, OR $0.27/SHARE
* CAPSTAR FINANCIAL HOLDINGS - QTRLY NET INTEREST INCOME AFTER PROVISION FOR LOAN LOSSES $10.5 MILLION VERSUS $10.1 MILLION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
